  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ModuleHandlePosix</TypeRef> class is an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IModuleHandle">IModuleHandle</PageRef> implementation.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Linux and macOS. This type is used by non-Windows builds and owns modules opened with <TypeRef>dlopen</TypeRef>.
    </Paragraph>
